v: 78
t: "Wa…óiree Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, Kanko O Su…ìike on O wa…óanaali on …ìitteende ka nder Diina, Diina baaba moo…óon Ibraahiima ko Kanko inni on jul…ìe ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo Nulaa…óo on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi wonon seeditoytoo…ìe e hoore yim…ìe …ìen. √ëii…ìnee e Julde nden totton Jakka on jogitee Alla, ko Kanko woni Gi…óo moo…óon mo∆¥∆¥ii gi…óo mo∆¥∆¥ii walloowo on"